They have larger, state-of-the-art FullView Display, dazzling high-tech body design in fashionable colors, crystal clear camera capability and many other features. It’s time to broaden your horizons with Gionee’s new S11 and S11 lite!#GioneeS11 #GioneeS11Lite #CaptureMoreBeauty

#GioneeS11 #GioneeS11Lite #CaptureMoreBeauty

Congratulations! Today is the day you reach the “next-level” in your smartphone “game” with Gionee’s new S11 lite. Finally! GIONEE’s new S11 has arrived. Now, Capture more of your world with S11’s four camera, a 16MP + 8MP dual camera in the front and 16MP + 5MP dual camera in the rear, delivering hardware-level real-time bokeh, Crystal Clear Zoom, and Group Beauty Selfie – pro-shooter capabilities that will win social media. Also, see more of your world in its 5.99-inch FullView Display and show more of your personal style with its distinctively designed four-sided curved body. #GioneeS11
